title: 2017 Angola Women's Handball League
text: The 2017 <a href="Angola%20Women%27s%20Handball%20League">Angola Women's Handball League</a> was the 38th edition, organized by the <a href="Federa%C3%A7%C3%A3o%20Angolana%20de%20Andebol">Federação Angolana de Andebol</a> ("Angolan Handball Federation"). The tournament was held from July 10–22, 2017 in <a href="Luanda">Luanda</a>, contested by 7 teams and won by <a href="C.D._Primeiro_de_Agosto_%28handball%29%23Primeiro_de_Agosto_Women.27s_Handball">Clube Desportivo Primeiro de Agosto</a>.
